body.description: A LUXE-urious pacifier that soothes babies, and parents alike! The PhysioForma Luxe Orthodontic Pacifier is a one-piece, 100% soft silicone pacifier with a softly textured shield and handle. Parents love that these pacifiers not only soothe but also provide benefits for baby’s breathing and orthodontic development.Parents love that PhysioForma pacifiers were developed, tested, and approved in partnership with an advisory panel of leading neonatologists, pediatricians, and orthodontists. The exclusive nipple design helps position the tongue forward to maintain an open airway and support baby’s physiological breathing. This is especially important at bedtime where it can help improve sleep quality and reduce irritability. Tiny ridges and an inclined nipple shape guide proper tongue placement while the unique angle and lateral curve of the nipple evenly distribute tongue pressure across the palate. Together, these important features support baby’s growing palate and orthodontic development. PhysioForma pacifiers adhere to the guidelines of the American Academy of Pediatrics and are accepted by 9 out of 10 babies.Babies love that the nipple is made from extra-soft, velvety silicone and has a satin-textured finish that helps baby keep the paci in their mouth for uninterrupted soothing. The just-like mom, skin-like feel is also ideal for breast-fed babies. Multiple ventilation holes promote air circulation and help reduce moisture buildup on baby’s soft, sensitive skin. Plus, the textured shield gently soothes baby during teething and the easy-to-grab handle is just the right size for either baby or parent to hold. Luxe pacifiers come in a variety of tones and textures from trending opaque shades to a crystal clear jewel-like finish. Choose from three sizes: 0-6m, 6-16m, or 16-24m. A reusable, sterilizing/carry case is also included.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: A Perfect Fit for Baby's Comfort Soft, flexible, high quality silicone pacifier is comfortable & breathable. A contoured, textured shield with 4 ventilation holes promote air circulation while helping to reduce moisture buildup on baby's delicate skin and a soft textured finish also soothes baby during teething. Plus, the extra-soft nipple helps baby stay latched - for more comfort & less slip! Exclusive Nipple Design for Baby's Breathing Clinical studies show PhysioForma pacifiers actively support baby's breathing. Our exclusive nipple (developed, tested & approved in partnership with an advisory panel of neonatologists, pediatricians & orthodontists) helps position baby's tongue forward to maintain an open airway. Orthodontic Design for Baby's Oral Development Unique angle and lateral curve of the nipple evenly distribute tongue pressure across baby's palate. Tiny ridges and an inclined nipple shape guide proper tongue placement. Together, these important features support baby's growing palate and teeth! One-Piece Construction for Safety and Hygiene Made from 100% food-grade silicone means there are no parts that can break apart & there is nowhere for germs to hide. One-piece pacifier adheres to the guidelines of the American Academy of Pediatrics. Another benefit of this design - an easy to grab handle for baby or parent to hold! Included Sterilizing Case for Cleanliness In addition to being handy storage for baby's pacis, you can also use the included case to quickly sanitize in the microwave in just 3 minutes!

Accessorize Your PhysioForma Luxe Choose Your Favorite Buddy Soft loveys make the perfect snuggle buddies and keep baby's paci close by. Attach pacifier to hand, tail or store in the roomy belly pocket. These cuddly friends are available in 4 friends: Bunny, Elephant, Fox, and Bear. Perfect for the paci stage and beyond. Long lasting. Machine washable. Fashionable Pacifier Clips Fashionable clips keep baby's pacis clean and within reach. Universal clips attach any style pacifier to baby's clothing, diaper bags, purses & more.
